      <access_permission_text>
        <para>When <register_link state="AArch64" id="AArch64-hcr_el2.xml">HCR_EL2</register_link>.E2H is 1, without explicit synchronization, access from EL2 using the mnemonic AFSR0_EL2 or AFSR0_EL1 are not guaranteed to be ordered with respect to accesses using the other mnemonic.</para>
